        "text": [
          "ه عن إسماعيل بن عيسى فقد رويته عن محمّد بن موسى بن المتوكّل- رضي اللّه عنه- قال: حدّثنا عليّ بن إبراهيم، عن أبيه، عن إسماعيل بن عيسى‌."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Everything in this book that is narrated from Isma'il ibn 'Isa has been transmitted by me from Muhammad ibn Musa ibn Al-Mutawakkil - may Allah (swt) be pleased with him - who said: Ali ibn Ibrahim narrated to us from his father, from Isma'il ibn 'Isa."
          ]
        }
